mtd: maps: pxa2xx-flash: fix memory leak in probe

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.163 by commit 1d0c2b762dad2b8dd166e17c0e90b88b86a3284f, it was introduced in version v2.6.24 by commit e644f7d6289456657996df4192de76c5d0a9f9c7. For more details please see the references link.
